{"arkId":"cl010363790","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010363790","modified ":"2025-08-25","title":"Grand bassin d\u0027apparat \u00e0 d\u00e9cor chinois en cama\u00efeu bleu et mangan\u00e8se","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Grand bassin d\u0027apparat \u00e0 d\u00e9cor chinois en cama\u00efeu bleu et mangan\u00e8se"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : Louis XIV (1643-1715) (Occident-\u003E\u00e9poque moderne = Ancien R\u00e9gime-\u003Edynastie des Bourbons)\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : vers 1660 - 1680","currentLocation":"non expos\u00e9","room":"","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1660,"endYear":1680,"imprecision":"vers","text":"2e moiti\u00e9 du XVIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Manufacture de Nevers","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 12546","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"bassin","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Grand bassin d\u00e9cor\u00e9 de couleurs de grand feu bleu de cobalt et brun violac\u00e9 de mangan\u00e8se sur \u00e9mail blanc bleut\u00e9, de forme circulaire l\u00e9g\u00e8rement creux et dot\u00e9 d\u0027une aile plate. La sc\u00e8ne montre deux chinois install\u00e9s \u00e0 l\u0027ombre d\u0027un petit arbre, occup\u00e9s \u00e0 d\u00e9guster des dattes dans un paysage, suscitant la convoitise d\u0027un flamant (\u00e0 gauche) et d\u0027un h\u00e9ron coiff\u00e9 (\u00e0 droite). Au devant, des rochers, feuillages et oiseaux se d\u00e9ploient largement sur l\u0027aile, comme l\u0027ensemble de la composition qui se lit verticalement et sans chercher \u00e0 compartimenter ni \u00e0 marquer les ailes ou le fond du plat. Au-dessus des personnages, deux b\u00e2timents, un temple et une maison, contribuent \u00e0 l\u0027effet de sym\u00e9trie d\u00e9j\u00e0 sensible dans la sc\u00e8ne centrale.","inscriptions":"","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Diam\u00e8tre","value":"49,2","displayDimension":"49,2 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Hauteur","value":"7","displayDimension":"7 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : fa\u00efence\r\nCouleur : bleu = bleue\r\nCouleur : brun-violet","placeOfCreation":"Nevers (Bourgogne-\u003ENi\u00e8vre)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Acquis par le donateur au marchand et expert Christophe Bils, Lyon, avril 2015 ; donation sous r\u00e9serve d\u0027usufruit \u00e0 titre anonyme en m\u00e9moire d\u0027Odile Flamant n\u00e9e Fiquet par l\u0027interm\u00e9diaire de la Soci\u00e9t\u00e9 des Amis du Louvre, 2016","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"Soci\u00e9t\u00e9 des Amis du Louvre","note":"","role":", Interm\u00e9diaire"}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"donation sous r\u00e9serve d\u0027usufruit","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date de comit\u00e9\/commission","value":"03\/02\/2016","startYear":2016,"endYear":2016},{"type":"date de l\u0027arr\u00eat\u00e9\/d\u00e9cision","value":"03\/02\/2016","startYear":2016,"endYear":2016},{"type":"date de l\u0027inscription sur l\u0027inventaire","value":"04\/02\/2016","startYear":2016,"endYear":2016}]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","longTermLoanTo":"","index":{"Mode d\u0027acquisition":[{"value":"donation sous r\u00e9serve d\u0027usufruit